Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸腐于野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊断于利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱之人 且赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐 因为我如此肥胖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要娶你这般细腰的女子才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我时常这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐厌恶肥胖之人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我们也学学弦之介大人与胧小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不住口 丈助 真没酒品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见朱绢小姐一脸为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可糟了 像是稍稍喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真美味 腌得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与甲贺的相比别有风味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定是盐的缘故 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺所购之盐均产自赤穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是喜欢不妨带些回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面盐仓中还贮有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有备无患啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐可是兵粮中不可或缺之物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助 不是让你小心慎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 无妨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后再无需隐藏保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗 阵五郎 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所言甚是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值此良机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请伊贺众看看我们练习的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那舞是准备在婚仪中才展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当日展现更精彩的技艺便可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技 权充伊贺甲贺和解之贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨以此笛此舞 愿世代永昌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您每次与胧小姐相见都在练习这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我与胧小姐相见时会做何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 我可说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 请原谅丈助的无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是甲贺最容易得意忘形的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢也并不介怀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真是有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为甲贺人会更凶神恶煞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了胧小姐讲那些面相凶恶的伊贺众的糗事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越有亲近感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想听多少我便说多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人若非亲近相处便不能互相了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 未见着在土岐岭遇到的那几位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得有些晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然出言相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究还是难以接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 定非此等原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是无可奈何之事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想必还有其他拒绝与我同席的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多花些时间 逐渐互相了解便可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甲贺卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你们伊贺锷隐一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方各怀可怖的忍法秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因长年宿怨而互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之见实是愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 你我携手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩断束缚两族的铁链
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天地真正广阔 让风声回荡两谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已将丈助关进那间客屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 卷轴的事切勿告诉他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被胧小姐察觉便糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢 我们也出手试探一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳他们此刻应当取了将监性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可天膳大人让我等不可妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此更应有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 鹈殿丈助就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铁板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特意用这种牢房想困住本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死我也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到被朱绢讨厌到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别有居心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起那时的表情真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 为何垂下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是累了吧 夜也深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并…并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸很红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何背对着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么 我没听清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我对这样的弦之介大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 果然还是去休息为好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没治的木头人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之没事便好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不顾羞耻前来相会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚宴上因为顾及伊贺众人的眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你走岔了真是抱歉 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么逃离这房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个嘛 就是全凭满腔爱念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难对付的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你的心意也与我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就当一夜我的新娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人叹服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来较量一下忍术吧 丈助阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若输了就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一夜你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会留情哦 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好歇息 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 朱绢在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿丈助 命丧于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太无情了吧 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若死了你要如何补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这死肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来胜负已分了 朱绢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就按我们说好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胧小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实是在下教而不改 又对朱绢小姐拉拉扯扯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于把她惹火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请您对弦之介大人保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请莫要再做这样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下对敢国神社发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\a6}敢国神社：位于三重县上野市，祭神为伊贺的鼻祖敢国津命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知你是哪位 伊贺之人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配尔等心灵、难以断绝的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其根深蒂固 方才的晚宴上我已有切身体会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望你们能斩断陈年宿怨的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今应是我等携手共书历史新章之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否相信我和胧小姐 助我们一臂之力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱绢 无论鹈殿大人的玩笑有多过火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动用忍术还是有些过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是盐仓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅 请您原谅 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下来 阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请莫要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想刺杀弦之介大人是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 阵五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐 如此下去阵五郎阁下会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准帮他 朱绢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才那杀气 她是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水 给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看 这不是雨夜阵五郎阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:20:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你莫非是想以这副模样刺杀弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我…水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 说吧 雨夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今甲贺与伊贺即将和解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还要杀弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水 给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你说 看 要多少水都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与服…服部家的…不战之约解…解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 跟服部家的约定？然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 伊贺与甲贺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺与甲贺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺与伊贺的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法之争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 我是不会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺十人众之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹈殿丈助 命丧于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨雾笼罩的甲贺村落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶气自北方逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引领他们的是残忍的邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰然老木所思为何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇袭 那是忍者的常用之道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍谷的北之街头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今化为血之泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 basilisk 甲贺忍法帖

